node.text:
Three takeaways:
1. Fran is *never* “Friendly” 🤪
2. Run through the finish line before you sprawl out on the floor.
3. No matter how well you executed a workout, you’re always going to say you think you could’ve gone faster 🙃 That’s why we love CrossFit am I right- always improvements to be made 😈
•••
🎥: @jtwiseguy

node.text:
sleep is ALWAYS a huge priority to me, you guys know that 😎 (sleep queen 😴👸🏻). leading into the Games, it’s even MORE IMPORTANT! my body tends to be a little more restless from the volume of training, which is why I depend so much on my @beam dream to knock me out 🙏🏼
